reviews.content:
#AndhaDhun Highly engaging thriller of the year, where it keeps getting twisted on every reel. A Blind piano artist who is not blind but becomes blind only to outsmart all non-blind over smart people around him. The best part of the movie is that it makes you think that you know what coming next only to make your predicament wrong.@ayushmannk fine performance as smart blind piano is very canny and few may contemplate his artistic skills with that of Legend #SanjeevKumar. 
@Tabuism is getting wiser and crisp actor as she is ageing. Her performance adds lots of fan following that what she had 2Decades back.
@Radhika_Apte a 
#ManavVij as a Cop, #AnilDhawan as yesteryear superstar and husband of Tabu, #AshwiniKalsekar as intimidating cop wife or any other co-artists support & contribute power in creation of this thriller.These kinds of movie needs soulful music but lesser songs, Songs are the only brakes in this perfect flawless movie. #SriramRaghavan has successful exposition and presentation of movie in such a manner that one will keep confabulating. His pre-visualisation of thriller also as a cowriter adds feathers to direction. 
#PoojaLadhaSurti has mastered the thriller movie editing. Soon a Directorial Debut can be expected.At the end, The Open ending of the movie will make people to think, dissect and discuss this fictitious thriller story
